<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='157:183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0084', 'WYG', '145-1a' );" name="145-1a" class="pb">[145-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:191'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='191:202'>　禮書卷一百四十六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='202:223'>　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　陳祥道　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='223:249'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0084', 'WYG', '145-2a' );" name="145-2a" class="pb">[145-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
